      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "bld",
        "text": "2 Chronicles 4:1-2",
        "children": [
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "verse-link",
            "text": "2 Chronicles 4:1-2",
            "children": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": ". ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "ital",
        "text": "Ten cubits the height thereof — ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "This was too high for the priests to lay the victims on it, without going up some kind of ascent; but as it was expressly commanded (",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "verse-link",
        "text": "Exodus 20:26",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": ") that they should not ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "ital",
        "text": "go up by ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "steps unto God’s altar; they doubtless ascended in some other way. ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "ital",
        "text": "Also he made a molten sea of ten cubits — ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "This and the following verses are explained ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "verse-link",
        "text": "1 Kings 7:23",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": ", &c.",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "p",
        "text": "",
        "children": [
          {
            "element": "br",
            "class": "",
            "text": "",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "element": "br",
            "class": "",
