            "children": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "bld",
        "text": "2 Chronicles 4:16",
        "children": [
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "verse-link",
            "text": "2 Chronicles 4:16",
            "children": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": ". ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "ital",
        "text": "Huram his father — ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "He is so called, because Solomon, it seems, usually called him by that name, out of that great respect which he bare to him for his excellent art, and the service which he did for him; it being usual to call great artists and inventors of things by this name. See ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "verse-link",
        "text": "Genesis 4:20-21",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": ".",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "p",
        "text": "",
        "children": [
          {
            "element": "br",
            "class": "",
            "text": "",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "element": "br",
            "class": "",
            "text": "",
            "children": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "bld",
        "text": "2 Chronicles 4:20-22",
        "children": [
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "verse-link",
            "text": "2 Chronicles 4:20-22",
            "children": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": ". ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "ital",
        "text": "That they should burn after the manner — ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "According to the prescription of God to them by Moses. ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "ital",
        "text": "The doors of the house were of gold — ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "To wit, in part. For they were not entirely of massy gold, but wood covered with plates of gold, ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "verse-link",
        "text": "1 Kings 6:31-35",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": ", and ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "verse-link",
        "text": "2 Kings 18:16",
        "children": []
