        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": " the altar made in the wilderness is described as measuring five cubits by five cubits, and in height three cubits. An altar three cubits high could perhaps be served from the ground, but one of ten cubits would require ",
        "children": []
