        "text": ". The altar of burnt-offering. Its preparation is passed over in ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "verse-link",
        "text": "1 Kings 6",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": " and 7, so that there it is only mentioned incidentally in connection with the consecration of the temple, ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "verse-link",
        "text": "1 Kings 8:22",
        "children": []
      },
      {
